
						TMTEST README



More on this project can be found at http://tmtest.berlios.de/


LICENSE

	LGPL.  See COPYING for more.


REQUIRES

	You need to install these libraries before building tmtest.

	libpcre:  http://pcre.org/


USES

	These files are used in the development of tmtest, but are
	do not need to be installed prior to compling it.

	pcrs:     http://www.oesterhelt.org/pcrs/
	re2c:     http://re2c.org/


INSTALL

	make
	make install prefix=/usr/local

	Defaults to installing in your home directory, ~/bin.  Use
	"prefix" to tell the install script where to put the files.

